#

Roasted Carrots with Honey

35 min
$3
80 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishEasyHealthy

Description

Sweet and tender roasted carrots glazed with honey and a sprinkle of salt.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 1 lb
  • honey: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • pepper: 1/4 tsp
